snippet.title: Crackdown 3 First Look
snippet.description:
Stop a ruthless criminal empire as a super-powered Agent of justice in Crackdown 3’s hyper-powered sandbox of mayhem and destruction, from original creator Dave Jones.

For more information, pleaes visit: www.xbox.com/crackdown and www.crackdown.com
